Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.31,0:01:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你死掉就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.23,0:01:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你这种人…死掉最好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.22,0:02:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.16,0:02:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(620,000)\u1}无 法 忘 记 的 思 念
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.03,0:02:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安 凛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.55,0:02:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安 为什么今天没叫我起床呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.46,0:02:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为今天是假日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.73,0:02:23.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下哦 我马上去把味噌汤热过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.90,0:02:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必啦 我跟亚沙前辈有约
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.48,0:02:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要出门吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.84,0:02:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 所以我不吃早饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.29,0:02:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.33,0:02:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.98,0:02:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 趁凛出门的这段时间来打扫洗衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.77,0:02:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉姆也来帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.21,0:03:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然在旅行回程的途中发生车祸…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.16,0:03:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土见夫妇也一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.74,0:03:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有芙蓉先生一个人扶养女儿一定很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.07,0:03:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说土见家的孩子也要一起照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.14,0:03:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起了 小凛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.09,0:03:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫就拜托你了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.54,0:03:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.84,0:03:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.92,0:03:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫！ 枫！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.65,0:03:50.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小枫！ 小枫…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.32,0:03:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令千金入院已经过了二周了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.01,0:03:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲的死对她打击好像很大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.65,0:04:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就好像是拒绝再活下去一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.49,0:04:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医生…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.07,0:04:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.33,0:04:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给她活下去的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.48,0:04:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给她活着的目标的话 就一定能…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.24,0:04:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小枫 你听的到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.95,0:04:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨的事令你很悲伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.03,0:04:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还有些事情没告诉你…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.62,0:05:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实阿姨的死…都是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.27,0:05:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人看家觉得很寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.79,0:05:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我硬要他们赶回家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.28,0:05:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后就在回程中发生了车祸…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.51,0:05:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…小枫?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.80,0:05:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.50,0:05:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这话...是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.72,0:05:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.92,0:05:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.84,0:05:40.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  枫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.44,0:05:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了 太好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.86,0:06:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今天开始这就是你的房间了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.22,0:06:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去把大件行李给搬过来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.26,0:06:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等安顿好了跟枫一起下来吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.03,0:06:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.48,0:06:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.73,0:06:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢走 小心点噢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.99,0:06:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安 小枫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.23,0:06:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.85,0:06:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的习题作了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.29,0:06:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.75,0:06:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 凛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.44,0:07:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边的生活过的还习惯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.63,0:07:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.86,0:07:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…枫你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.99,0:07:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟凛相处的还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.16,0:07:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.69,0:07:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.23,0:07:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我弄掉了 帮我捡起来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.17,0:07:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我捡起来…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.30,0:07:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.77,0:08:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.07,0:08:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么妈妈死了 而你却还活着?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.71,0:08:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝不原谅你 你死掉就好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.92,0:08:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你这种人… 死掉了最好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.29,0:09:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…妈妈？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.11,0:09:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是妈妈寄给我的…在她死那天？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.24,0:09:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等小枫的病好了 下次我们再一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.23,0:09:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,病?  我的病…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.29,0:09:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 枫她还在发烧…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.93,0:09:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像又复发了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.49,0:09:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得能去旅行真是不好意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.12,0:09:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.04,0:09:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题 她说马上赶回来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.29,0:09:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不要紧吗 妈妈很担心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.44,0:09:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起了 凛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.24,0:10:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.76,0:10:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事 不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.16,0:10:11.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.67,0:10:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你骗了我么…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.17,0:10:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.05,0:10:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这都是我的错…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.31,0:10:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.86,0:10:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我…害死的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.27,0:10:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.74,0:10:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…是我…将妈妈…害死的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.90,0:10:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.56,0:11:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.05,0:11:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.81,0:11:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.06,0:11:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…对不起…对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.25,0:12:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我能活着都是托凛的福
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.98,0:12:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我为了凛…为了凛…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.71,0:12:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.06,0:12:38.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为两位还是一起喝～这“恋爱热带果汁”最好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.03,0:12:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.98,0:12:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请给我们一般的冰淇淋就好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.87,0:12:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太遗憾了…那么请稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.16,0:12:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来伊羽前辈打工的店 不是会谣言满天飞吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.64,0:12:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你讨厌跟我产生谣言吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.01,0:13:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…而且从那之后我一直在反省
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.38,0:13:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.50,0:13:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚沙前辈 你有在听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.26,0:13:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没在听耶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.25,0:13:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请听我说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.55,0:13:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我去一下洗手间…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.54,0:13:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈？ 亚沙前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.22,0:13:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小沙！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.42,0:13:32.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.37,0:13:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小沙！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.39,0:13:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事…就这样像公主般的抱着我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.38,0:13:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.72,0:13:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是有点晕眩罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.27,0:13:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是昨天熬夜的关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.33,0:13:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的没关系吗  能站起来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.03,0:13:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 我希望让凛抱着我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.48,0:13:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.05,0:14:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回家 今天很早呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.83,0:14:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为亚沙前辈身体不适 所以送她回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.19,0:14:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈她?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.87,0:14:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽听她说是熬夜的关系…没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.90,0:14:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…吃过饭了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.53,0:14:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么一说我都还没吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.58,0:14:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上去准备 请在客厅看电视稍等一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.86,0:14:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦 普莉姆拉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.53,0:14:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.98,0:14:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 一起玩游戏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.15,0:14:42.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去换件衣服 等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.21,0:14:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小沙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.66,0:14:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.51,0:15:01.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 我拿药过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.80,0:15:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 放那边就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.27,0:15:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别太过勉强 小凛他会很担心的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.55,0:15:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.54,0:15:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我晚饭时会叫你 你好好休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.21,0:15:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.38,0:15:36.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖啡不喝了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.75,0:15:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.96,0:15:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛 明天有什么计划吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.90,0:15:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.15,0:15:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要跟莉姆一起去购物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.95,0:15:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋季的服装要添购一下了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.56,0:15:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.36,0:15:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就久违地大家一起去外面吃顿饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.00,0:15:59.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.25,0:16:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去接
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.13,0:16:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.13,0:16:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我是亚沙前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.18,0:16:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我已经没事了 真对不起噢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.95,0:16:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 算是作为赔罪好了…下次换我约你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.21,0:16:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.53,0:16:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我当然会去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.78,0:16:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次就换前辈请客
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.03,0:16:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 那就明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.10,0:16:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是亚沙前辈打来的?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.52,0:16:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 她说明天要去看电影
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.65,0:16:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 那购物…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.60,0:16:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,购物?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.53,0:16:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.00,0:16:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了吗 枫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.46,0:16:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.00,0:16:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.79,0:17:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几点会回来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.09,0:17:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.41,0:17:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会准备好晚餐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.06,0:17:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们就先吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.62,0:17:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.11,0:17:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.10,0:17:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫…不去购物吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.44,0:17:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去了 我不想去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.50,0:17:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛…好慢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.76,0:17:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是跟亚沙前辈在一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.81,0:17:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为凛他满脸欢喜的出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.35,0:17:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.37,0:17:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来那么幸福的凛 我还是第一次见到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.82,0:18:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.59,0:18:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛觉得幸福的话 就好了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.45,0:18:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要凛幸福的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.95,0:18:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫你就没关系吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.50,0:18:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然啦 照顾凛的生活就是我生存的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.46,0:18:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要凛觉得幸福 这样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.21,0:18:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.11,0:18:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 是凛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.20,0:18:49.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫吗 我要在亚沙前辈家吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.21,0:18:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天不用准备我的份了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.17,0:18:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚麻小姐 这样太多了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.75,0:18:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小凛还年轻 一定都吃的下的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.35,0:19:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就放弃抵抗吧 味道我能保证的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.78,0:19:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.19,0:19:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 今晚我会很晚回家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.04,0:19:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.95,0:20:10.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫…对不起…昨天问了很奇怪的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.71,0:20:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…枫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.47,0:20:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.71,0:20:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫…枫!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.27,0:20:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨 打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.94,0:20:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必客气 快上来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.30,0:20:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就恭敬不如从命…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.47,0:20:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.73,0:21:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你回去…请你回去…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.20,0:21:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.03,0:21:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我回去!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.94,0:21:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去回去!不准你再踏进这个家一步!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.04,0:21:12.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.45,0:21:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把凛…还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.40,0:21:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.01,0:21:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.01,0:21:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要! 为什么 这是为什么!？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.24,0:21:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫 你到底怎么了 冷静一点!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.86,0:21:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 放开我!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.73,0:21:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我适可而止…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.97,0:21:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你这种人…死了最好!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.57,0:21:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.52,0:21:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么能这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.21,0:21:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凛…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.51,0:22:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈…亚沙前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.86,0:22:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吧 亚沙前辈…前辈!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.69,0:22:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈 亚沙前辈 前辈!!
